drm/nouveau: Replace the iturbt_709 prop with the standard COLOR_ENCODING prop

Replace the ad-hoc iturbt_709 property with the new standard
COLOR_ENCODING property. Compiles, but not tested.

v2: Fix typos (Ilia)

